523
01:01:22,592 --> 01:01:26,653
"She was a religious woman,
without the joy of Catholicism

524
01:01:27,063 --> 01:01:30,032
"which, if need be,
covers the marks on the wall

525
01:01:30,166 --> 01:01:32,225
